modules.description: This module enables representing and manipulating dynamic values of diverse types through a GADT-like structure, supporting equality checks, comparisons, hashing, and pretty-printing alongside builders for wrapping primitives, collections, and algebraic data. It revolves around a unified dynamic type that models records, variants, and results via structured constructors, allowing type-safe construction and deconstruction of heterogeneous data. Such capabilities are particularly useful for generic programming, serialization frameworks, or dynamic data processing where structured, extensible value handling is required.
